34:22   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Lewi 23.15-21, 39-43; Kub 28.26-31
34:23 “Uko umwaka utashye, abagabo bo muri mwe bose bajye baboneka imbere y'Umwami Uwiteka Imana y'Abisirayeli, ibihe bitatu.
34:24 Kuko nzakwirukanira amahanga akaguhunga, nkāgūra ingabano zawe, kandi nta wuzifuza igihugu cyawe, nujya ujya kuboneka imbere y'Uwiteka Imana yawe ibihe bitatu, uko umwaka utashye.
